lkfa is the oldest of Polish science fiction and fantasy award, although less known than the Janusz A. Zajdel Award. It is awarded by the Silesian Fantasy Club (lski Klub Fantastyki), the oldest of still-active Polish fandom organizations. The award has been first presented in 1983. 
